{"tid":2036102,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講曬 噴巴士擋風玻璃/倒後鏡割唔割","createTime":"2020-05-26T09:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T09:57:37.000Z","uid":227309,"like":22,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b4fa17b3f259e78fadb345162dbf7134dba353c3","tid":2036102,"uid":227309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:18:15.000Z","msg":"基於安全理由，如果巴士擋風玻璃/倒後鏡嘅視線受阻，巴士就一定要停喺度，唔可以再行。<br />\n<br />\n用噴漆噴一噴玻璃，最多用你十秒，假設一條主要幹道有四條行車線，你只係需要用四十秒噴四架巴士，就可以癱瘓成條幹道，效率可謂極高。<br />\n<br />\n不過有兩個問題。<br />\n<br />\n第一，要小心車cam同附近途人，唔好咁唔小心比人影到相。<br />\n<br />\n第二，巴士公司係無辜嘅。<br />\n<br />\n一句講曬，割定唔割？<br />\n<br />\n效率至上，一齊噴巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SDmBj00.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSDmBj00.png&h=5b9d6363&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過GTA V啲AI嘅智商好似無咁高，有啲懷疑噴完架巴士個司機都會照行。Anyway，咁樣做真係好危險，所以打機先好咁樣玩，真實生活千其唔好咁樣做。"},{"pid":"5b701a124dc0ce78f16386e6d339b2a54fad6aa4","tid":2036102,"uid":227309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:18:45.000Z","msg":"樓主心水清"},{"pid":"62c084461beebffd79e63657e24a8079313e35de","tid":2036102,"uid":227309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:19:03.000Z","msg":"樓主人格分裂？"},{"pid":"e368975e7ef536b672099efed153ad5e37c60a38","tid":2036102,"uid":227309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:21:43.000Z","msg":"十連一"},{"pid":"91faf14547595c54753b361673267b86d74ac13f","tid":2036102,"uid":227309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:22:23.000Z","msg":"十連二"},{"pid":"c39a4de6dd93c826268b4691be6bb169c2e9f435","tid":2036102,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:22:30.000Z","msg":"黎明行動做過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no